{"tid":1005004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"土耳其禮儀課：年輕女性不該舔冰淇淋","createTime":"2019-02-02T01:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T06:16:53.000Z","uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f40dbcda6a92faaa2024bcec6f8848066872c0cc","tid":1005004,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T01:58:23.000Z","msg":"土耳其禮儀課：年輕女性不該舔冰淇淋<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2688401\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2688401&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2XWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=dae3d2d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2688401&h=3ab33b4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2688401</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕土耳其伊斯坦堡開設為期2個月的「禮儀課程」，教導年輕女學生「如何成為伊斯坦堡淑女」，內容包括在公開場合不應該舔舐冰淇淋，奇怪的性別歧視課程在推特上被網友砲轟。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，伊斯坦堡巴格希勒市（Bagcilar）對此指出，「市政青年中心提供的講座，將傳授在公共場合如何表現出良好的舉止」，<span style=\"color: red;\">當局認為女性不應該在公開場合舔舐冰淇淋，卻沒有解釋食用冰淇淋、冰棒的不合理之處</span>，讓網友們認為這樣的保守課程相當愚蠢。<br />\n<br />\n此外，<span style=\"color: red;\">「禮儀課程」的內容還提到，女性不應該再公共場所嚼食口香糖，也不鼓勵她們使用某些俚語，更不可以在搭公車時講電話講太久、早上妝化得太濃，其中一項大忌是詢問剛認識的男人是否已經結婚了，或是向初相見的男子詢及小孩數量。</span><br />\n<br />\n課程講師阿達（Arzu Arda）指出，禮儀被載入「土耳其的宗教、傳統和文化」，他認為現今社會對禮儀的認知有所減弱，因此希望藉由課程加以強化該層面的觀念；但外國推特網友們得知土耳其官方開設這種只針對女性的課程，均感到相當不可思議，認為這些內容已經侵犯到女性的基本人權。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e559e12a70a2a0cd658edc43cf50c083cf8c9e77","tid":1005004,"uid":203417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:02:14.000Z","msg":"完全冇進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f294bb883b2ff571330d4724585245fe8c0fb7fc","tid":1005004,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb054628e4a323d9993fb028d5c7ddb50fb3afc0","tid":1005004,"uid":77968,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:16:08.000Z","msg":"應該舔龜頭"},{"pid":"e5015e3cd529912e31162d84889c3e5135a5e7d9","tid":1005004,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:23:09.000Z","msg":"駛唔駛用刀叉呀火雞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557e91329bf5fb2352ecc02b7496352b79482db3","tid":1005004,"uid":71133,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:23:28.000Z","msg":"d回教男人幾撚猥瑣先可以咁都聯想到"},{"pid":"302210b5dea250dbabd039e7a4e4dc04fcacfb13","tid":1005004,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:24:41.000Z","msg":"出軌要浸豬籠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae420321423c4708cf7d7f94622b03b693f0036b","tid":1005004,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:29:22.000Z","msg":"如何成為伊斯坦堡淑女<br />\n<br />\n唔做淑女都得嫁。冇歧視女性成份"},{"pid":"3b450134c448fd0dfa55b53e31767c19719afbb5","tid":1005004,"uid":197337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:34:08.000Z","msg":"年輕女性不該舔冰淇淋，應該含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d2e0efce8168554333ca5f9b85da3997a31f7a","tid":1005004,"uid":58852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T06:09:16.000Z","msg":"男人都唔應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043588aef0f5d4d5f8845a3f0535dfed157725f1","tid":1005004,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T06:10:43.000Z","msg":"有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c63425d2482752eb34b7205f0a2f9c4296badc7","tid":1005004,"uid":191730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB